// Purpose:		Returns a boolean flag to indicate whether the receiver has a Stock
//				Booking Reference.
//
// Parameters:	None
//
// Returns:		True if the receiver has a Stock Booking Reference, otherwise false.
//
// Changed On	Changed By	Reason
