Parameters:			

Return Value:		

Date			Who		Reason
15 July 2024	navlw1	ChangedRequest 63839: NSW | OnePort - Uniqueness of Inward and External Code 

*/

vars

begin
	if self.myVoyageProcess = null then
		return false;
	endif;
	
